    "text": "(This measure has not been amended since it was introduced. The summary of that version is repeated here.)\n\nFairness in Nursing Home Arbitration Act - Provides that a pre-dispute arbitration agreement between a long-term care facility and a resident (or anyone acting on the resident's behalf) shall not be valid or specifically enforceable."
